c: 9
v: 93
t: "Nabiyow cagalah dambii kee sahi gita edde-lem usun duudak gaddaloolah anuk gaaduk kok wadirroowaanamih idini koo essera maray salaadaay agabuuy lakmisa marâ luk Raaqaanamat leedeeh ruffu iyyeeh Yalli aben dambitteh lubbitte kak alfe mara kinni, tokkel usun ellecabo sinnik toomem yaaxige mara hinnon jihaadak Raaqeenimih sabbatah"